=== LAB 07: (Review)
OBJECTIVE
In this lab, you will practice to set Ownership 

SETUP
Before beginning the lab, follow these steps to prepare the hosts indicated
(these steps assume a cleanly installed host OS and VMs): 

STEPS:


  # Creating groups and granting them ownership to documents.


---
- hosts: localhost
  tasks:
  - group:
      name: eng
      state: present
  - group:
      name: swa
      state: present
  - user:
      name: patrick
      groups: eng
      state: present
  - user:
      name: percilla
      groups: eng
      state: present
  - user:
       name: paul
       groups: swa
       state: present 
	
	1. Group swa can view and execute the directory /lang/english in the eng group.
	2. Group eng can also view and execute the directory /lang/swahili on swa group.
	3. Create an empty file nouns in english directory and only the user who created the file is allowed to delete this file. 
